Text: "The whore's honey pours, she leaves her sent on all of man. Death was her name, and the perfume that looms. She begged for battle, and with love I obliged her moaning pleas for pain. For in war, Aries always finds pleasure, and hungers for more without measure." - Ehyeh Asher Ehyeh (a.k.a. Cide Twiy)
